(110, 1, '2021-05-03 12:31:51', '2021-05-03 09:31:51', '<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:pb/accordion-item {\"initiallyOpen\":true,\"scroll\":true,\"uuid\":1107} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-pb-accordion-item c-accordion__item js-accordion-item no-js is-open\" data-initially-open=\"true\" data-click-to-close=\"true\" data-auto-close=\"true\" data-scroll=\"true\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\"><h2 id=\"at-1107\" class=\"c-accordion__title js-accordion-controller\" role=\"button\">Member Benefits</h2><div id=\"ac-1107\" class=\"c-accordion__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are many reasons to become a member of the BIEA and join our research community:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>As a member based outside Africa, you receive online access to our high-impact peer reviewed journals&nbsp;<em>Azania: Archaeological Research in Africa</em>; and&nbsp;<em>Journal of Eastern African Studies</em>&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Africa-based scholars receive online access either via BIEA membership or for free via Taylor &amp; Francis’ STAR programme:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://authorservices.taylorandfrancis.com/publishing-your-research/choosing-a-journal/supporting-authors-in-emerging-regions/star-eligible-countries/\">https://authorservices.taylorandfrancis.com/publishing-your-research/choosing-a-journal/supporting-authors-in-emerging-regions/star-eligible-countries/</a>)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>As a member you are able to join exclusive member-only events and study groups, and receive advanced warning about all of our upcoming events via our weekly member’s news bulletin. Covid has led us to move our events to online platforms, and we will continue to offer this option in the future, even when face-to-face meetings are possible again.&nbsp;</li><li>Members can apply for all the funding and opportunities provided by the BIEA, including our bi-annual thematic grants awards and our unique funding programmes such as our grant-writing and research dissemination awards.&nbsp;</li><li>Members are entitled to use our facilities in Nairobi for events and research, including hiring our events spaces, using our well-stocked library, and hiring our field equipment.&nbsp;</li><li>As a member of the BIEA you join a rich, diverse community of researchers working across Africa on subjects from across the humanities and social science, opening possibilities for networking and collaborating and expanding research horizons.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:pb/accordion-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:freeform -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-pb-accordion-item c-accordion__item js-accordion-item no-js\" data-initially-open=\"false\" data-click-to-close=\"true\" data-auto-close=\"true\" data-scroll=\"true\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\">\n<h2 id=\"at-1108\" class=\"c-accordion__title js-accordion-controller\" role=\"button\">Member Categories</h2>\n<div id=\"ac-1108\" class=\"c-accordion__content\"></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:freeform -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Annual membership of the British Institute in Eastern Africa is open to all, and runs from January to December each year. There are several categories of membership (all members receive online access to our journals):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:freeform /--></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:pb/accordion-item {\"scroll\":true,\"uuid\":1102} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-pb-accordion-item c-accordion__item js-accordion-item no-js\" data-initially-open=\"false\" data-click-to-close=\"true\" data-auto-close=\"true\" data-scroll=\"true\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\"><h2 id=\"at-1102\" class=\"c-accordion__title js-accordion-controller\" role=\"button\">How to Join</h2><div id=\"ac-1102\" class=\"c-accordion__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Annual membership of the British Institute in Eastern Africa is open to all, and runs from January to December each year with the relevant membership rate payable at any point during the year.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To be eligible for our discounted membership rate, students and retirees will need to provide proof of status before completing the membership process.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Select your membership category from the table above.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can pay here using&nbsp;PayPal.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can pay here using&nbsp;credit / debit card.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can pay here via&nbsp;M-Pesa&nbsp;using the following information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Go to&nbsp;<strong>M-PESA&nbsp;menu</strong>, select “<strong>Lipa na M-PESA“</strong></li><li>Select&nbsp;<strong>“Pay Bill“</strong></li><li>Select “Enter&nbsp;<strong>Business no.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>329329</strong></li><li>Select “Enter&nbsp;<strong>Account no.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>0102814345900</strong></li><li>&nbsp;Enter the&nbsp;<strong>amount</strong></li><li>Enter your&nbsp;<strong>M-PESA PIN</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Confirm</strong></li><li><strong>Standard Chartered Bank</strong>&nbsp;will also send you a&nbsp;<strong>confirmation SMS.</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please complete the membership form&nbsp;here&nbsp;and email this, along with proof of status (for students / retirees) and proof of payment to&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:membership@biea.ac.uk\">membership@biea.ac.uk</a></strong>&nbsp;to complete your membership process. Your BIEA login details will be sent to you in reply.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have any membership queries, please contact&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:membership@biea.ac.uk\">membership@biea.ac.uk</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:pb/accordion-item -->', 'Members Portal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'members-portal', '', '', '2021-05-03 12:44:38', '2021-05-03 09:44:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/biea/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0),
